      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">21/11/79 ¶  ¶ Enclosed I am sending you, dear Mr Tepper, the names of your plants that have just arrived. The silky-haired  ¶ Billardiera ¶  I described already as  ¶ B. sericophora ¶  in  ¶ Linnaea ¶...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">79.11.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">21/11/79</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">Hierbei sende ich Ihnen, lieber Herr Tepper, die Namen Ihrer eben angelangten Pflanzen. Die seidenhaarige Billardiera beschrieb ich bereits als B. sericophora in der Linnaea 1852, aber hernach schien sie mir mit der gewöhnlichen B. cymosa zusammen zu laufen. Die Mittelformen kommen nicht immer auf einem begrenzten Gebiet wie das Ihrigen vor, u man findet das Unhaltbare einer angenommenen Art oft erst in fernen Gegenden aus. Das Solanum mit eiformigen Früchten ist S. fasciculatum FvM., früher von mir publicirt. Die Art mit kuglichen Beeren = S. simile. Die Unterschiede zwischen beiden sollten durch Beobachtung in freier Natur von Ihnen genauer festgestellt werden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Züfallig finde ich, dass Ardrossen ein brittischer geograph. Name ist.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Da das südl. Ende Ihre Halbinsel 50 Meilen von Ihnen entfernt ist, mag es dort eine etwas andere Vegetation geben. Es wäre wichtig, das vermuthliche Manna-Insekt von Euc. viminalis zu erlangen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Varietäten, wie der Eutaxien, können sich durch Generationen aus Samen erhalten. Bedenken Sie nur, wie wenig sich die Varietäten des Kohls, des Getreides &amp;c &amp;c in Cultur ändern.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vom aufrechten <name key="Exocarpus">Exocarpus</name> möchte ich gern reife Früchte sehen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundlichst grüssend </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21/11/79</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed I am sending you, dear Mr Tepper, the names of your plants that have just arrived. The silky-haired <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Billardiera</seg> I described already as <seg style="font-style: italic; ">B. sericophora</seg> in <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Linnaea</seg> of 1852,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. 1853; see B53.04.01, p. 371.</p>
               </note> but afterwards it seemed to me to converge with the common <seg style="font-style: italic; ">B. cymosa</seg>. The middle forms do not always occur in a restricted region like yours, and one discovers the untenable one of an accepted species often first in distant regions. The <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Solanum</seg> with oval fruits is <seg style="font-style: italic; ">S. fasciculatum</seg> FvM., publicized previously by me. The species with spherical berries = <seg style="font-style: italic; ">S. simile</seg>. The differences between the two should be determined more exactly by you through observation in the countryside.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By chance I find that Ardrossan is a British geographical name.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Tepper was living at this time in Ardrossan, SA; the original Ardrossan is in Ayrshire, Scotland.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Because the southern end of your peninsula is 50 miles away from you, there may be a somewhat different vegetation there. It would be important to get the supposed manna insect of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Eucalyptus%20viminalis">Eucalyptus viminalis</name>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Varieties like the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Eutaxia">Eutaxia</name>s</seg> can remain through generations from seeds. Just consider how little the varieties of cabbage, wheat &amp;c &amp;c alter in cultivation.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I would like to see ripe fruits of the erect <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Exocarpus">Exocarpus</name>
               </seg>. </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Friendliest greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Billardiera%20cymosa">Billardiera cymosa</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Billardiera%20sericophora%20">Billardiera sericophora </name>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20viminalis">Eucalyptus viminalis</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eutaxia">Eutaxia</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Exocarpus">Exocarpus</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Solanum%20fasciculatum">Solanum fasciculatum</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Solanum%20simile">Solanum simile</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
